title: Woman Walking Facing Right

adjectives: Used to represent movement, walking, or exercise.
verbs: Depicts a woman walking or strolling to the right.
nouns: A woman shown walking, often used to convey exercise, travel, or casual movement.

description: A woman shown walking toward the right. Represents walking, exercise, movement, or travel. Can also be used in contexts related to hiking, fitness, or casual strolling.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the woman walking facing right emoji depicts a woman in mid-stride, rendered with realistic proportions, soft gradients, and subtle movement shading. It symbolizes activity, movement, and health-conscious behavior.
